sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Django
    participant Broker as Mosquitto
    participant Client as MQTT Client
    participant Postgres

    User->>Django: POST /api/service/{service_name}/command/
    Django->>Broker: Publish command (QoS 1, retain=false)
    Django->>Postgres: Store command log
    Broker->>Client: Deliver command
    Client->>Client: stop = pause polling/publishing only
    Client->>Client: stay connected and subscribed
